high_descs: Go to the left and stand in front of the fridge.
Open the door of the fridge and take the plate from the middle of the top shelf.
Close the fridge and go to the right and stand at the counter in front of the microwave.
Put the plate in the microwave, turn it on, open the microwave, and take the plate out and shut the door.
Go right and approach the cabinet above the sink.
Open the cabinet above the sink, put the plate on the bottom shelf, and shut the door.

Take the tray on the left out of the fridge.
Bring the tray to the stove on the right.
Heat the tray in the microwave above the stove.
Bring the heated tray to the sink on the right.
Put the tray in the cabinet above the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the fridge so you're in front of it and facing it.
Open the fridge and pick up the plate that's in the middle of the top shelf and close the door.

Put the plate in the microwave and warm it up before getting it back out and closing the door.

Open the cupboard that's above the sink and put the warm plate in there.
